When you cast a {c_important}Marksman{/c} Skill, you gain a stack of {c_important}Precision{/c}. You gain an additional stack if that Skill Critically Strikes, once per cast. 

When you reach {c_number}[SF_1]{/c} stacks of {c_important}Precision{/c}, your next {c_important}Marksman{/c} Ultimate or Core Skill is a guaranteed Critical Strike and deals {c_number}[SF_10 * 100|%x|]{/c} increased Critical Strike Damage, consuming all stacks of {c_important}Precision{/c}. This damage is further increased by {c_number}[{SF_6} * 100|x%|]{/c} of your Critical Strike Damage bonus. 

Current Bonus: {c_number}[{SF_7} * 100|1%x|]{/c}
